---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="AI Tools - Vibe Prolog" description="AI coding tools and automation workflows used to build Vibe Prolog">
  <div class="hero">
    <h1>AI TOOLS & AUTOMATION</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">HOW MULTIPLE AI CODING TOOLS WORK TOGETHER TO BUILD VIBE PROLOG</p>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <section>
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>
        Vibe Prolog is built entirely with AI code generation, demonstrating what's possible when
        you leverage multiple AI coding tools working together. This page documents the tools and
        workflows used throughout the development process.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Primary Development Tools</h2>

      <div class="tool-card">
        <h3>Claude Code</h3>
        <p>
          The main development interface for iterative coding. Claude Code provides an interactive
          CLI that integrates with the codebase, allowing for natural language programming and
          complex multi-step tasks.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Interactive development sessions</li>
          <li>Code generation and refactoring</li>
          <li>Test writing and debugging</li>
          <li>Documentation generation</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-card">
        <h3>Claude Sonnet 4.5</h3>
        <p>
          The core AI model powering the implementation. Handles complex architectural decisions,
          algorithm implementations, and maintains code quality throughout the project.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Core Prolog engine implementation</li>
          <li>Parser design and unification algorithm</li>
          <li>Built-in predicate implementation</li>
          <li>Comprehensive test suite development</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Automation & Workflows</h2>

      <div class="tool-card">
        <h3>Kilocode</h3>
        <p>
          Automated issue-to-PR workflow tools that streamline the development process by handling
          the entire cycle from issue creation to pull request submission.
        </p>

        <h4><code>fix-issue-with-kilocode</code></h4>
        <p>Automates the complete workflow of fixing a GitHub issue:</p>
        <ol>
          <li>Creates a new branch based on the issue</li>
          <li>Runs <code>kilocode</code> against the issue content</li>
          <li>Commits and pushes any changes</li>
          <li>Opens a pull request with generated title and body</li>
        </ol>

        <div class="code-example">
          <pre><code>fix-issue-with-kilocode 123</code></pre>
        </div>

        <h4><code>address-pr-comments-with-kilocode</code></h4>
        <p>Automatically addresses review comments on pull requests:</p>
        <ol>
          <li>Fetches PR details and review comments</li>
          <li>Checks out the PR branch</li>
          <li>Runs <code>kilocode --auto</code> to address comments</li>
          <li>Commits changes with AI-generated commit message</li>
          <li>Pushes updates to the PR</li>
        </ol>

        <div class="code-example">
          <pre><code>address-pr-comments-with-kilocode 456</code></pre>
        </div>

        <p class="tool-requirements">
          <strong>Requirements:</strong> <code>uv</code>, <code>git</code>, <code>gh</code>,
          <code>kilocode</code>, <code>llm</code>, and <code>OPENAI_API_KEY</code> environment variable
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-card">
        <h3>gh-pr-helper</h3>
        <p>
          A utility that fetches GitHub PR comments and formats them in markdown suitable for
          AI coding agents. Makes it easy to feed review feedback back into the AI development cycle.
        </p>

        <h4>Features</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Fetches both general PR comments and inline code review comments</li>
          <li>Organizes comments by file and line number</li>
          <li>Includes code context (diff hunks) for inline comments</li>
          <li>Filters out metadata not useful for AI agents</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="code-example">
          <pre><code>gh-pr-helper nlothian/Vibe-Prolog/pull/10 > comments.md</code></pre>
        </div>

        <p class="tool-requirements">
          <strong>Requirements:</strong> Python 3.12+, <code>gh</code> (GitHub CLI)
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Supporting Tools</h2>

      <div class="tool-list">
        <div class="tool-item">
          <h4>GitHub Copilot</h4>
          <p>Provides real-time code suggestions and completions during development (via Cursor IDE)</p>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-item">
          <h4>LLM CLI</h4>
          <p>Command-line interface for large language models, used for commit message generation and text processing</p>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-item">
          <h4>UV</h4>
          <p>Fast Python package and project management tool, replacing traditional pip/virtualenv workflows</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Development Workflow</h2>

      <div class="workflow">
        <div class="workflow-step">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h4>Issue Creation</h4>
            <p>Create a GitHub issue describing the feature, bug fix, or improvement</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="workflow-step">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h4>Automated Implementation</h4>
            <p>Run <code>fix-issue-with-kilocode</code> to automatically create branch, implement, and open PR</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="workflow-step">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h4>AI Review</h4>
            <p>AI tools review the PR, run tests, and provide feedback on code quality</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="workflow-step">
          <div class="step-number">4</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h4>Address Comments</h4>
            <p>Run <code>address-pr-comments-with-kilocode</code> to automatically address review feedback</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="workflow-step">
          <div class="step-number">5</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h4>Merge</h4>
            <p>Once all checks pass and review is satisfied, merge the PR</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Installation & Setup</h2>

      <p>To use these tools in your own projects:</p>

      <h3>Kilocode Tools</h3>
      <div class="code-example">
        <pre><code>cd ai-tools
uv run kilocode/fix-issue-with-kilocode --help
uv run kilocode/address-pr-comments-with-kilocode --help</code></pre>
      </div>

      <h3>gh-pr-helper</h3>
      <div class="code-example">
        <pre><code>cd ai-tools/gh-pr-helper
chmod +x gh-pr-helper
./gh-pr-helper nlothian/Vibe-Prolog/pull/10</code></pre>
      </div>

      <p>
        See the individual README files in the <code>ai-tools/</code> directory for detailed
        installation instructions and requirements.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>The Philosophy</h2>

      <p>
        This project demonstrates that AI code generation is most powerful when multiple tools
        work together in a coordinated workflow:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Interactive AI</strong> for complex problem-solving and architecture</li>
        <li><strong>Automated workflows</strong> for repetitive tasks and process automation</li>
        <li><strong>Human oversight</strong> for quality control and strategic decisions</li>
        <li><strong>Continuous iteration</strong> to improve code quality over time</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        By combining these approaches, we can achieve higher code quality and faster development
        than any single approach alone.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="cta">
      <h2>Want to Contribute?</h2>
      <p>
        Tool vendors: Want to add your AI coding tool to this project? We'd love to try it!
        Open a PR or issue on GitHub.
      </p>
      <a href="https://github.com/nlothian/Vibe-Prolog" class="neon-button primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        VIEW ON GITHUB
      </a>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-2xl) 0;
    border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(255, 0, 128, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    color: var(--color-electric-magenta);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-shadow:
      0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 128, 0.6),
      0 0 40px rgba(255, 0, 128, 0.4);
    animation: neonPulse 2s infinite;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--color-cyber-blue);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.4);
  }

  .content {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--color-cyber-blue);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.5);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.4);
  }

  h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-electric-magenta);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 0, 128, 0.4);
  }

  h4 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-acid-green);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.3);
  }

  p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  ul, ol {
    margin: var(--space-md) 0;
    padding-left: var(--space-xl);
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .tool-card {
    background-color: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.6);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.5);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.3);
    transition: all var(--duration-normal) var(--easing-elastic);
  }

  .tool-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.6);
    border-color: rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.8);
  }

  .tool-card h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: var(--color-electric-magenta);
  }

  .code-example {
    background-color: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.8);
    border: 1px solid rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.3);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    margin: var(--space-md) 0;
    overflow-x: auto;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.2);
  }

  .code-example pre {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .code-example code {
    font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-acid-green);
  }

  .tool-requirements {
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.1);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-toxic-yellow);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .tool-requirements strong {
    color: var(--color-toxic-yellow);
    text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.4);
  }

  .tool-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .tool-item {
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-acid-green);
    background-color: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.4);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.2);
    transition: all var(--duration-fast);
  }

  .tool-item:hover {
    background-color: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.6);
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.4);
  }

  .tool-item h4 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: var(--color-acid-green);
  }

  .tool-item p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .workflow {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .workflow-step {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .step-number {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 3rem;
    height: 3rem;
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-electric-magenta);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-electric-magenta);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    box-shadow:
      0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 128, 0.4),
      inset 0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 128, 0.1);
  }

  .step-content {
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .step-content h4 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    color: var(--color-cyber-blue);
  }

  .step-content p {
    margin-top: var(--space-xs);
    color: rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.8);
  }

  .step-content code {
    background-color: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.8);
    color: var(--color-acid-green);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
    font-size: 0.9em;
    border: 1px solid rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.2);
  }

  .cta {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    background-color: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.6);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 0, 128, 0.5);
    margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
    box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(255, 0, 128, 0.3);
  }

  .cta h2 {
    border-bottom: none;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .cta p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .neon-button {
    background: transparent;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-electric-magenta);
    color: var(--color-electric-magenta);
    padding: 16px 40px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 18px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    box-shadow:
      0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 128, 0.4),
      inset 0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 128, 0.1);
    transition: all var(--duration-normal) var(--easing-elastic);
  }

  .neon-button:hover {
    background: var(--color-electric-magenta);
    color: var(--color-void-black);
    box-shadow:
      0 0 60px rgba(255, 0, 128, 0.8),
      0 0 100px rgba(255, 0, 128, 0.4);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3rem);
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    h3 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .workflow-step {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-sm);
    }

    .step-number {
      width: 2.5rem;
      height: 2.5rem;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .tool-card {
      padding: var(--space-md);
    }

    .neon-button {
      padding: 12px 30px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
  }
</style>
